	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=162776><span id= >aerondor</span></a><br><span id=notbold>3 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Only one specialisation can go over 50.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you get the wrong one (for most clerics, that means, not alteration) there is a quest you can do to reset all your specialisations.<br><br>Best idea is to train up to over 50 when you first get the skill.  An hour in the newbie zone casting minor healing over and over should get you a lot of the way towards that.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
